      "title": "Bandula assigned to look after education",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Dr. Bandula Gunawardena, Minister of Transport, Highways and Mass Media was sworn in as the Acting Minister of Education before President Gotabhaya Rajapaksa today (27).",
        "Dr. Bandula Gunawardena has been appointed to oversee the Ministry of Education due to the official visit of the Minister of Education Susil Premajayantha.",
        "Dr. Bandula Gunawardena was the Minister of Education from 2010 to 2015."
      ],
